{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Challenge solutions","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/Guide/CSS/Getting_started/Challenge_solutions","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>このページは、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS\">CSS&nbsp;Getting Started</a> チュートリアルにあるチャレンジの解答例です。これ以外の解答も考えられます。以下の章名はチュートリアルページのタイトルと一致します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_をなぜ用いるか","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps/How_CSS_works\" id=\"Why_use_CSS_Colors\" title=\"MDC\">CSS をなぜ用いるか</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"CSS をなぜ用いるか"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"colors","title":"Colors","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dd>\n  Without looking up a reference, find five more color names that work in your stylesheet.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  CSS&nbsp;supports common color names like <code>orange</code>, <code>yellow</code>, <code>blue</code>, <code>green</code>, or <code>black</code>. It also supports some more exotic color names like <code>chartreuse</code>, <code>fuschia</code>, or <code>burlywood</code>. See <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\">CSS Color value</a> for a complete list as well as other ways of specifying colors.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"どのように_css_は動作するのか","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps/How_CSS_works\" id=\"How_CSS_works_DOM_inspector\" title=\"MDC\">どのように CSS は動作するのか</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"どのように CSS は動作するのか"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_inspector","title":"DOM inspector","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_2\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  In DOMi, click on a <small>STRONG</small> node. Use DOMi's right-hand pane to find out where the node's color is set to red, and where its appearance is made bolder than normal text.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_2\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  In the menu above the right-hand pane, choose <strong>CSS Rules</strong>.&nbsp; You see two items listed, one that references an internal resource and one that references your stylesheet file. The internal resource defines the <strong>font-weight</strong> property as <code>bolder</code>; your stylesheet defines the <strong>color</strong> property as <code>red</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"接続と継承","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Cascade_and_inheritance\" id=\"Cascading_and_inheritance\" title=\"MDC\">接続と継承</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"接続と継承"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"inherited_styles","title":"Inherited styles","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_3\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Change your stylesheet so that only the red letters are underlined.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_3\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  Move the declaration for underlining from the rule for <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> to the one for <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a>. The resulting file looks like this:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">strong</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> underline<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>\n<p>Later sections of this tutorial describe style rules and declarations in greater detail.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"セレクター","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Selectors\" id=\"Selectors\" title=\"MDC\">セレクター</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"セレクター"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"second_paragraph_blue","title":"Second paragraph blue","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_4\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Without changing your HTML file, add a single rule to your CSS file that keeps all the initial letters the same color as they are now, but makes all the other text in the second paragraph blue.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_4\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  Add a rule with an ID selector of <code>#second</code> and a declaration <code>color:&nbsp;blue;</code>, as shown below:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">#second</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n  A more specific selector, <code>p#second</code> also works.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"both_paragraphs_blue","title":"Both paragraphs blue","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_5\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Now change the rule you have just added (without changing anything else), to make the first paragraph blue too.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_5\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  Change the selector of the new rule to be a tag selector using <code>p</code>:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>\n<p>The rules for the other colors all have more specific selectors, so they override the blue of the paragraph.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"読みやすい_css","title":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Readable_CSS\" title=\"MDC\">読みやすい CSS</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"読みやすい CSS"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"commenting_out_a_rule","title":"Commenting out a rule","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_6\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Comment out part of your stylesheet, without changing anything else, to make the very first letter of your document red.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_6\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  One way to do this is to put comment delimiters around the rule for <code>.carrot</code>:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/*\n.carrot {\n  color: orange;\n}\n*/</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"文章のスタイル","title":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Text_styles\" title=\"MDC\">文章のスタイル</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"文章のスタイル"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"big_initial_letters","title":"Big initial letters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_7\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Without changing anything else, make all six initial letters twice the size in the browser's default serif font.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_7\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  Add the following style declaration to the <code>strong</code> rule:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code>  <span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200% serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n  If you use separate declarations for <code>font-size</code> and <code>font-family</code>, then the <code>font-style</code> setting on the first paragraph is <em>not</em> overridden.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"色","title":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Color\" title=\"MDC\">色</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"色"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"three-digit_color_codes","title":"Three-digit color codes","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_8\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  In your CSS file, change all the color names to 3-digit color codes without affecting the result.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_8\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  The following values are reasonable approximations of the named colors:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">strong</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f00<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* red */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ddf<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* pale blue */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200% serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.carrot</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fa0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* orange */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.spinach</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #080<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* dark green */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #00f<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* blue */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"コンテンツ","title":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Content\" title=\"MDC\">コンテンツ</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"コンテンツ"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"画像の追加","title":"画像の追加","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"チャレンジ\">\n  チャレンジ</dt>\n <dd>\n  各行の初めに画像を表示するように、スタイルシートに一つルールを追加してください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"解答\">\n  解答</dt>\n <dd>\n  次のルールをスタイルシートに追加します:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p:before</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">\"yellow-pin.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"リスト","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Styling_text/Styling_lists\" id=\"Lists\" title=\"MDC\">リスト</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"リスト"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"小文字のローマ数字","title":"小文字のローマ数字","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"チャレンジ_2\">\n  チャレンジ</dt>\n <dd>\n  スタイルシートに一つルールを追加して、リスト項目に i から v のローマ数字で番号をつけてください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"解答_2\">\n  解答</dt>\n <dd>\n  <code>lower-roman</code> のリストスタイルを使って、リスト項目に一つルールを定義します:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">li</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">list-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> lower-roman<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"大文字","title":"大文字","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"チャレンジ_3\">\n  チャレンジ</dt>\n <dd>\n  見出しを括弧内の大文字のアルファベットで識別するように、スタイルシートを変更してください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"解答_3\">\n  解答</dt>\n <dd>\n  body 要素（見出しの親要素）にはカウンターをリセットするルールを、見出しにはカウンターを表示し増加させるルールを追加します:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* numbered headings */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">counter-reset</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> headnum<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">h3:before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"(\"</span> <span class=\"token function\">counter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>headnum<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> upper-latin<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token string\">\") \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">counter-increment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> headnum<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ボックス","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/The_box_model\" id=\"Boxes\" title=\"MDC\">ボックス</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"ボックス"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"海の境界線","title":"海の境界線","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"チャレンジ_4\">\n  チャレンジ</dt>\n <dd>\n  スタイルシートに一つルールを追加して、リスト項目全体を囲むような広い枠を作り、海を連想するような色にしてください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"解答_4\">\n  解答</dt>\n <dd>\n  次のルールでこの効果を出せます:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">ul</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px solid lightblue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"レイアウト","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/CSS_layout\" id=\"Layout\" title=\"MDC\">レイアウト</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"レイアウト"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"デフォルトの画像位置","title":"デフォルトの画像位置","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"チャレンジ_5\">\n  チャレンジ</dt>\n <dd>\n  サンプル文書 <code>doc2.html</code> を編集し、次のタグを文書の末尾近く、<code>&lt;/BODY&gt;</code> のすぐ前に追加します: <code> &lt;IMG id=\"fixed-pin\" src=\"Yellow-pin.png\" alt=\"Yellow map pin\"&gt;</code> 画像がどこに現れるか、推測してみてください。それからブラウザを更新して、正しかったかどうかを確認してください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"解答_5\">\n  解答</dt>\n <dd>\n  画像は2番めのリストの右側に現れます。<br>\n  <img alt=\"pin_placement.png\" class=\"internal default\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/4718/=pin_placement.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"画像位置の固定化","title":"画像位置の固定化","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"チャレンジ_6\">\n  チャレンジ</dt>\n <dd>\n  スタイルシートにルールを追加して、文書の右上に画像を置くようにしてください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"解答_6\">\n  解答</dt>\n <dd>\n  次のルールでできます:\n  <pre class=\"notranslate\">#fixed-pin  {\n  position:fixed;\n  top: 3px;\n  right: 3px;\n} </pre>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"表","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Styling_tables\" id=\"Tables\">表</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"表"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"borders_on_data_cells_only","title":"Borders on data cells only","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_9\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Change the stylesheet to make the table have a green border around only the data cells.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_9\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  The following rule puts borders around only <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a> elements that are inside the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code></a> element of the table with <code>id=demo-table</code>:\n  <pre class=\"notranslate\">#demo-table tbody td {\n  border:1px solid #7a7;\n}\n</pre>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"メディア","title":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/CSS/Getting_Started/Media\" id=\"Media\" title=\"MDC\">メディア</a>","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"メディア"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"separate_print_style_file","title":"Separate print style file","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_10\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Move the print-specific style rules to a separate CSS file and import them into your <code>style4.css</code> stylesheet.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_10\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  Cut and paste the lines between <code>/* print only */</code> and <code>/* end print only */</code> into a file named <code>style4_print.css</code>. In style4.css, add the following line at the beginning of the file:\n  <pre class=\"notranslate\">@import url(\"style4_print.css\") print;\n</pre>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"heading_hover_color","title":"Heading hover color","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_11\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Make the headings turn blue when the mouse pointer is over them.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_11\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  The following rule achieves the desired result:\n  <pre class=\"notranslate\">h1:hover {\n  color: blue;\n}\n</pre>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"move_box_to_the_right","title":"Move box to the right","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"challenge_12\">\n  Challenge</dt>\n <dd>\n  Change the script so that the square jumps to the right by 20 em when its color changes, and jumps back afterwards.</dd>\n <dt id=\"solution_12\">\n  Solution</dt>\n <dd>\n  Add lines to modify the <code>margin-left</code> property. Be sure to specify it as <code>marginLeft</code> in JavaScript. The following script achieves the desired result:\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">// JavaScript demonstration\nfunction doDemo (button)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  var square = document.<span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"square\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  square.style.backgroundColor = <span class=\"token string\">\"#fa4\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  square.style.marginLeft = <span class=\"token string\">\"20em\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  button.<span class=\"token function\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"disabled\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>clearDemo<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 2000<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> button<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">function clearDemo (button)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  var square = document.<span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"square\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  square.style.backgroundColor = <span class=\"token string\">\"transparent\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  square.style.marginLeft = <span class=\"token string\">\"0em\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  button.<span class=\"token function\">removeAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"disabled\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps/How_CSS_works\" id=\"Why_use_CSS_Colors\" title=\"MDC\">CSS をなぜ用いるか</a>","id":"css_をなぜ用いるか"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps/How_CSS_works\" id=\"How_CSS_works_DOM_inspector\" title=\"MDC\">どのように CSS は動作するのか</a>","id":"どのように_css_は動作するのか"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Cascade_and_inheritance\" id=\"Cascading_and_inheritance\" title=\"MDC\">接続と継承</a>","id":"接続と継承"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Selectors\" id=\"Selectors\" title=\"MDC\">セレクター</a>","id":"セレクター"},{"text":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Readable_CSS\" title=\"MDC\">読みやすい CSS</a>","id":"読みやすい_css"},{"text":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Text_styles\" title=\"MDC\">文章のスタイル</a>","id":"文章のスタイル"},{"text":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Color\" title=\"MDC\">色</a>","id":"色"},{"text":"<a href=\"/\" id=\"Content\" title=\"MDC\">コンテンツ</a>","id":"コンテンツ"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Styling_text/Styling_lists\" id=\"Lists\" title=\"MDC\">リスト</a>","id":"リスト"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/The_box_model\" id=\"Boxes\" title=\"MDC\">ボックス</a>","id":"ボックス"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/CSS_layout\" id=\"Layout\" title=\"MDC\">レイアウト</a>","id":"レイアウト"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Styling_tables\" id=\"Tables\">表</a>","id":"表"},{"text":"<a href=\"/ja/docs/CSS/Getting_Started/Media\" id=\"Media\" title=\"MDC\">メディア</a>","id":"メディア"},{"text":"JavaScript","id":"javascript"}],"summary":"このページは、 CSS Getting Started チュートリアルにあるチャレンジの解答例です。これ以外の解答も考えられます。以下の章名はチュートリアルページのタイトルと一致します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Challenge solutions","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/guide/css/getting_started/challenge_solutions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/guide/css/getting_started/challenge_solutions/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Guide","title":"開発者ガイド"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Guide/CSS/Getting_started/Challenge_solutions","title":"Challenge solutions"}],"pageTitle":"Challenge solutions - 開発者ガイド | MDN","noIndexing":false}}